      "writtenOn": "2018-04-07T06:13:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I guess the small texture data up front scheme would require some sort of dispatch to the renderer here.\n\nAnother way would be to create another context in the same share group as the renderer, and have the loader thread issue GL commands directly, but IMO that can wait until we need to be async loading more kinds / quantity of data.",
